## HashMap.entries() method

Returns a new Iterator object that contains an array of `[key, value]` for each element in the hash map.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
entries(): IterableIterator<[K, V]>;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

IterableIterator&lt;\[K, V\]&gt;
